---
const faqs = [
    {
        q: "How many projects can I host for free?",
        a: "Unlimited. There are no restrictions on the number of independent documentation projects you can manage within a single Astrodex hub. You can organize them by folder and deploy them all as one unified site."
    },
    {
        q: "How does it help with SEO?",
        a: "Astrodex is built for performance and semantic clarity. It generates automated sitemaps, supports custom meta tags per page, and maintains perfect Lighthouse scores, which are all critical ranking factors for Google."
    },
    {
        q: "Is it really 100% free to host?",
        a: "Yes. Because Astrodex generates a static site, you can host it on platforms like GitHub Pages, Vercel, or Netlify's free tiers forever. You only pay for your domain name if you choose to use a custom one."
    },
    {
        q: "Can I use custom domains for each project?",
        a: "Astrodex is designed as a unified hub (e.g., docs.yourcompany.com/project-a). While it typically shares one domain, the internal routing structure is perfectly optimized for search engines to index each project independently."
    },
    {
        q: "How difficult is it to maintain?",
        a: "Zero maintenance. There is no database or backend server to manage. Your documentation lives as Markdown files in your Git repository. Updates are handled through simple Git commits and automatic deployments."
    }
];
---

<section class="py-24 border-t border-border-muted bg-midnight">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-text-dim mb-4">FAQ</h2>
            <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-text-main tracking-tighter uppercase">Common Questions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
            {faqs.map(faq => (
                <details class="group border border-border-subtle rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.01] overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:border-white/20">
                    <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
                        <span class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-text-dim group-open:text-white transition-colors uppercase tracking-tight">
                            {faq.q}
                        </span>
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-open:rotate-180 group-open:bg-white group-open:text-black transition-all duration-500 border border-border-muted">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down text-[10px]"></i>
                        </div>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content px-6 pb-8 pt-2">
                        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-text-muted leading-relaxed font-light border-l border-white/10 pl-6">
                            {faq.a}
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
            ))}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .faq-content {
        animation: slideDown 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }

    @keyframes slideDown {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    summary::-webkit-details-marker {
        display: none;
    }
</style>